net.dougvalenta.scriptorium

Interface Inscribable<I,THIS extends Inscribable<I,THIS>>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type to pass to consumers
    THIS - this type

    public interface Inscribable<I,THIS extends Inscribable<I,THIS>>
    Implementers may choose to pass another type <I> to consumers, e.g. a broader type that does not have methods consumers should not call.
    Author:
    Doug Valenta
